title: Bunkercast XX: Steve Wyche
itunes:title: Bunkercast XX: Steve Wyche
description:
A bunker filled with heroes - Dan Hanzus, Chris Wesseling, Marc Sessler and Gregg Rosenthal are joined by Steve Wyche to cover the news around the nfl. A few new teams released new uniforms and they're not all that bad. Plus, Steve sat down with Tua Tagvailoa and thinks he'd make a good fit with the Chargers.
